		`

		<description><![CDATA[I came to Canada to escape a childhood&mdash;and a nation&mdash;consumed with lies]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="1200" height="1200" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/Rogan_USCanada__1200_01.jpg" class="webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image" alt="A photo hangs on the wall of a man with a cowboy hat and boots, holding a whip. On the wall also hangs an American flag, and what appears to be a military jacket." loading="lazy" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;max-width: 100%;" link_thumbnail="" /><p><head></p>
<style>
.single-post.hitmag-full-width.th-no-sidebar  #masthead {position: revert !important;}
.su-row.relatedlinks {display:revert;} .su-animate.fadeInRight {float:right;}
